ance, and refine the design as needed."}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"common-scenarios-in-system-design"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Common Scenarios in System Design"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"URL Shortener"}]},{"type":"text","value":": Focus on unique URL generation, database storage, and high availability."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Messaging System"}]},{"type":"text","value":": Emphasize real-time delivery, scalability, and persistence."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"E-Commerce Platform"}]},{"type":"text","value":": Handle user authentication, inventory management, and payment processing."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Video Streaming Platform"}]},{"type":"text","value":": Optimize content delivery, buffering, and scalability."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"conclusion"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Conclusion"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"System design is both an art and a science. By mastering its principles, you can create applications that are scalable, reliable, and efficient—ensuring a seamless experience for users and long-term success for your organization."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Thank you so much for reading. If you found it valuable, consider subscribing for more such content every week. If you have any questions or suggestions, please email me your comments or feel fr